display.description: Read only, with a default verification timer of 30 seconds. Verification timer has a minimum value of 1 and maximum value of 31536000. Write-back timer must have value of 0 or be null.
Read-write, with a default verification timer of 8 hours and default write-back timer of 1 hour. Verification timer and write-back timer have a minimum value of 1 and maximum value of 31536000.
